If you are listening to this and you are frustrated because your most deeply researched, carefully constructed, high-binding insights gain zero traction on your feed,

416
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:51,680
you need to understand that you are not failing.

417
00:42:51,680 --> 00:43:02,480
You are not a defective communicator because you cannot distill a complex systemic analysis into a highly recomposable three-slide carousel.

418
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:05,620
Your ideas are not supposed to achieve velocity.

419
00:43:05,960 --> 00:43:12,920
They are fundamentally mathematically incompatible with the structural constraints of the distribution machine.

420
00:43:13,120 --> 00:43:16,880
The lack of virality is not an indictment of your cognitive architecture.

421
00:43:17,180 --> 00:43:20,180
