422
00:43:20,180 --> 00:43:26,400
You have successfully engineered a jigsaw piece in an environment that only tolerates Lego bricks.

423
00:43:26,740 --> 00:43:32,600
So stop attempting to optimize your deepest cognitive frameworks for algorithmic distribution.

424
00:43:33,320 --> 00:43:40,080
It is a game you can only mathematically win by actively dismantling the very value you are attempting to share.

425
00:43:40,880 --> 00:43:45,500
Accepting invisibility in exchange for structural truth is not a defeat.

426
00:43:45,720 --> 00:43:47,960
It is a calculated regime exit.

427
