We are rapidly delegating our reading, our summarizing, our synthesis, and our cognitive generation to artificial intelligence models.

433
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:31,000
We really are.

434
00:44:31,340 --> 00:44:40,160
And the critical reality is that these large language models are entirely trained on the massive, creeped aggregate of the internet.

